<script context="module">export const metadata = {"text":"<p>I don&#39;t mean to pick on these frameworks, because they&#39;re all doing really interesting and cool stuff — these are just particularly notable examples. And they would all point out elements of Svelte&#39;s programming model that they&#39;re not keen on.</p>\n<p>Nor am I telling you what to think — I encourage you to play around with all of these frameworks and develop your own opinions. I&#39;m just telling you what <em>I</em> think, and what I think is that your scientists were so preoccupied with whether they could, they didn&#39;t stop to think if they should.</p>\n","title":"Your scientists were so preoccupied","classnames":"","styles":[]};</script>

